    "description": "仿生机器人模拟器是一款未来概念的FPS游戏，在游戏中你将扮演一个负责操控宇宙殖民飞船的仿生机器人。<br>你的职责是在完成主线任务的同时，尽可能减少损失。除了主线活动之外，每部分游戏都会有随机事件发生，让每部分新的环节都有不同的游戏过程。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>电力供应</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891250/extras/225d0fdce6a434bbc6a89b1f201535a9.poster.avif?t=1747386600\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891250/extras/225d0fdce6a434bbc6a89b1f201535a9.webm?t=1747386600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891250/extras/225d0fdce6a434bbc6a89b1f201535a9.mp4?t=1747386600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>管理好你的殖民飞船的能源系统。密切关注电力需求。你的飞船会根据推进力、主动防护系统的功率、氧气发生器以及其他参数来消耗能量。<br>如果出现麻烦，你需要关闭相应的飞船模块来做出反应。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>殖民者</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891250/extras/614ee6092973051797f660ebef060e80.poster.avif?t=1747386600\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891250/extras/614ee6092973051797f660ebef060e80.webm?t=1747386600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891250/extras/614ee6092973051797f660ebef060e80.mp4?t=1747386600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你所负责管理的飞船上满载着36个低温胶囊。胶囊里有处于冬眠状态的杰出科学家和精选的育种者。你的工作是保证这些对象的健康，并让胶囊的技术状况保持良好。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>植物园</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891250/extras/6a9e587bbf08643a074d90ebff9f5972.poster.avif?t=1747386600\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891250/extras/6a9e587bbf08643a074d90ebff9f5972.webm?t=1747386600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891250/extras/6a9e587bbf08643a074d90ebff9f5972.mp4?t=1747386600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>殖民飞船拥有自给自足的调控系统。氧气和额外的食物可由植物来提供，为植物生长提供合适的气候条件也在你的职责范围内。控制好各项参数，如空气湿度、温度和水化水平。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>导航</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891250/extras/b116fbb2995fbc96f891d9bd0e78abcd.poster.avif?t=1747386600\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891250/extras/b116fbb2995fbc96f891d9bd0e78abcd.webm?t=1747386600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891250/extras/b116fbb2995fbc96f891d9bd0e78abcd.mp4?t=1747386600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>根据不断变化的条件，调整飞行的路线。在游戏过程中，你会遇到一些随机事件，比如流星雨造成的破坏、逃离行星引力、系统故障或探索废弃的小行星等。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>医疗</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891250/extras/2b0693935c684ede504f1eaa366340f8.poster.avif?t=1747386600\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891250/extras/2b0693935c684ede504f1eaa366340f8.webm?t=1747386600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891250/extras/2b0693935c684ede504f1eaa366340f8.mp4?t=1747386600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>进入冬眠的殖民者可能会患上与因他们在太空中长期飞行有关的疾病。有些人会出现病症，或许需要你的医疗护理。管理实验室的检测活动并给出切实可行的治疗方案。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>机修</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891250/extras/39a5bfb7ad6f3c8e7b5ae57a8c79a296.poster.avif?t=1747386600\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891250/extras/39a5bfb7ad6f3c8e7b5ae57a8c79a296.webm?t=1747386600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891250/extras/39a5bfb7ad6f3c8e7b5ae57a8c79a296.mp4?t=1747386600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>管理好飞船的技术指标也是你的职责之一。你要及时修补损坏的部件，并根据不同的技术难题灵活地做出相应的处理决定。",
